 This is a post market, prospective, multicenter, non-randomized, single arm study of the EnligHTN cent Renal Denervation System.

 Approximately 500 subjects with uncontrolled hypertension will undergo renal artery ablation at approximately 40 investigational sites located internationally and will be followed up to five (5) years post procedure.

